213
00:17:25,039 --> 00:17:26,480
Even if the times are tough,

214
00:17:26,799 --> 00:17:28,279
even if we've lost our support,

215
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:29,880
bringing them here

216
00:17:30,079 --> 00:17:32,279
