258
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,440
And also,

259
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,839
whenever I think about

260
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:30,640
people like Wang Mutian,

261
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:32,000
who have all betrayed us,

262
00:20:34,079 --> 00:20:35,839
